Sentencas: Power generation characteristics of fuel cells was greatly improved by using La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.115Co0.085O3 as electrolyte.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using Co doped La(Sr)Ga(Mg)O3 perovskite oxide with notably high power density at intermediate temperature

Sentencas: In particular, the maximum power density attained a value of 1.53 and 0.50 W cm(-2) at 1073 and 873 K, respectively, in an H-2-O-2 cell when the thickness of electrolyte was 0.18 mm.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using Co doped La(Sr)Ga(Mg)O3 perovskite oxide with notably high power density at intermediate temperature
